The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Sri Lanka run riot
                                                   Sri Lanka run riot
                      
	Karachi: Mahela Jayawardene scored his first Test century against Pakistan, guiding Sri Lanka to a commanding 406 for three on the first day of the first Test on Saturday.         
	Jayawardene, in the process, became the 10th man to score a century against all other Test-playing nations.           (AP)                                                                                                                   
